<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>电子邮件</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.kainonly.com/assets/uikit/css/uikit.min.css"/>
    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="uk-background-muted">
<div class="uk-container uk-padding">
    <h1 class="uk-heading-small">{{.Name}}</h1>
</div>
<div class="uk-container uk-padding uk-tile uk-tile-default">
    <h3 class="uk-text-uppercase">你好，{{.User}}</h3>
    <p class="uk-text-normal">管理后台验证码为：</p>
    <h1 class="uk-heading-large uk-heading-bullet">{{.Code}}</h1>
    <p class="uk-text-warning">5分钟内有效，逾期后您需要重新获取，切勿将验证码提供给他人</p>
    <hr class="uk-divider-icon">
    <p class="uk-text-normal uk-text-muted">本邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复！</p>
</div>
<div class="uk-container uk-padding">
    <p class="uk-text-small uk-text-italic">Copyright © {{.Year}} {{.Name}}. All rights reserved.</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>